title: FPS using Nvidia GTX 970M?
body: I currently am using a GTX 970M GPU with Intel i7-6700HQ Processor, i turn shadows off and the rest of my video settings is at High quality settings. With uncapped, i am getting average of 100~140 (during teamfights). My previous computer had GTX 770M with Intel i7-4700HQ processor and was getting higher FPS than this. Is there something wrong with my machine?

replies.body:
Hey there,

That doesn't sound right, could you provide the model number of both laptops so I can look into the specs.

You could try altering your power settings under Windows and your Graphics card's panel to be **High Performance**
